data.description: Big backyard barbeques with family and friends.  A large vegetable and flower garden to nourish the farm to table dream.  Ample room for playful pets, active children or just relaxing around a firepit.  If any of these scenarios are what you wish for in a fully privacy fenced backyard then this house is a must see!  The xeri-scaped, low maintenance, front yard allows for plenty of time to create the backyard of your dreams.  The well maintained bungalow sports an open concept  living-dining area that opens to the covered patio in the backyard.  The galley style kitchen opens directly to the garage and dining area, allowing for a smooth flow through the home.  This compact, move in ready home is surprisingly roomy and is primed for a new owner to introduce their sytle to it!
